snippet.title: 100% Orange Juice Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Gameplay preview of 100% Orange Juice.
Characters from Acceleration of Suguri, Flying Red Barrel: A Diary of Little Aviator, ChristmaShu~, Sora, and QP Shu~ come together with all-new characters to duke it out in 100% Orange Juice.

100% Orange Juice is a goal-oriented boardgame played by Orange_Juice's all-star cast.
Localized by Fruitbat Factory.
http://fruitbatfactory.com
